Which application segment dominates the terpene resin market?
The pharmaceutical industry is the largest consumer of terpene resin, followed by the food and beverage industry.

What are the major challenges faced by the terpene resin market?
The market faces challenges such as fluctuating prices of raw materials and strict government regulations regarding the use of terpene resin in certain products.

Which regions are leading in the terpene resin market?
Currently, North America and Europe are the leading regions in the terpene resin market, with Asia-Pacific showing significant growth potential.

What are the popular types of terpene resin available in the market?
The most popular types of terpene resin include alpha-pinene, beta-pinene, and limonene, among others.

